00:30:13.396 --> 00:30:15.021
[GASPS]

494
00:30:15.022 --> 00:30:16.566
[THUNDER CRASHES]

495
00:30:17.400 --> 00:30:18.941
[GRUNTS]

496
00:30:18.942 --> 00:30:21.654
[♪♪♪]

497
00:30:23.364 --> 00:30:24.907
[YELLS]

498
00:30:35.418 --> 00:30:37.335
JASON:
<i>Emily once told me that</i>

499
00:30:37.336 --> 00:30:40.338
in her dorm room,
she resisted the demons,

500
00:30:40.339 --> 00:30:43.258
but at the hospital,
they overcame her.

501
00:30:43.259 --> 00:30:45.635
So she believed
that her actual possession

502
00:30:45.636 --> 00:30:47.263
began that night
at the hospital?

503
00:30:48.305 --> 00:30:50.932
Yeah. I think she did.

504
00:30:50.933 --> 00:30:52.517
And after that, things just went

505
00:30:52.518 --> 00:30:54.394
<i>from bad to worse.</i>

506
00:30:54.395 --> 00:30:56.397
[DISTORTED CHATTER]

507
00:30:58.691 --> 00:31:00.818
[GIRL LAUGHS]

508
00:31:08.576 --> 00:31:11.036
